Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:37.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:37.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
